   <body>
      <p>Qualifications &amp; Benefits feature enables you to add products or categories for which you want to provide benefits at the package level: products that are packaged instantly during the time of purchase. If the customers do not purchase any of the products which are a part of the package then they do not qualify for the Package Saving Program.</p>
      <p>A user can specify prices for the package as well as a-la-carte prices for each product included in the package.</p>
      <p>Products purchased will be counted towards package first so that package price will be used in billing. Excessive units will each receive the a-la-carte price.</p>
